Bloomberg's Tom Keene talks with 
 Grover Norquist , president, Americans for  Tax Reform , who sees 
states hemorrhaging money, cash as people move to states with 
lower tax rates. They speak on Bloomberg Television's 
"Surveillance Midday." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 01:30
 